"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[Gotosocial](https://github.com/superseriousbusiness/gotosocial) 真如其所说轻量级个人服务，5G存储的服务器安装完只占用了30%，剩下的空间估计还能用很久。加入了他们[项目交流群](https://app.element.io/#/room/#gotosocial:superseriousbusiness.org)，大佬指导很耐心，项目也有详细的[安装指导](https://docs.gotosocial.org/en/latest/installation_guide/binary/)，虽然存在一点点小错误。\\n\\n之前尝试搭建 [Misskey](https://github.com/misskey-dev/misskey) 但是存储占用太高了，小服务器容不下。但是在[已有实例](https://neko.ci/)中注册了 misskey 体验还是不错的，功能丰富。推荐一波：\\n\\n[https://neko.ci/](https://neko.ci/)\\n\\n这几天胡乱折腾了好久，该干活了！\",\"timestamp\":1641543514,\"title\":\"搭建轻量服务的 GoToSocial \"},\"digest\":\"rIsDnwgGjJzKescxSZha0g_Fttee7_LARo5V_-YUV7U\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0872437046E456BaAa75e99eDBBcC70fE3E77Bc8\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"mcB__8IWdqTuLxVnOqDf1QZ7pli-bCdjQmvpgUjqZBw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2Kt6dk6u00VORGyrOSmIGNM1LnlUyJpkaPzqfXLLU7E\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"3wtYzrDPicn2IRTce99HnLPx8h5GAHMVyoDO80uCRGzY2xp43vHRjWX6skDybzJ5onIr6gOpH0BJi3bTNrl0jg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x6a5ae9bce5cd38152691d425f8be6adf12942cf54426ca9539d2c0aee25d2d280bd3f5cb20fd208987909123189d1eeccd3baee0c57702c392acebc528652d501c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"mcB__8IWdqTuLxVnOqDf1QZ7pli-bCdjQmvpgUjqZBw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2Kt6dk6u00VORGyrOSmIGNM1LnlUyJpkaPzqfXLLU7E\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"NWSOl-jgtq_WwJ38F3gNfSKTcBRuxeT_HjIJJA1-jnM\"}"